Description: # PiDi Display Plugin for PIL-based image output
        
        This plugin renders album art and transport information to a PIL image for display.
        
        0.1.0
        -----
        
        * Improve CPU usage by only redrawing if a visual change has occured
        
        0.0.2
        -----
        
        * Performance enhancements
        * Fix progress bars
        
